# Git Workflow

## Branch Naming
`{USERNAME}/{TICKET}-{summary}`
- `andrescrz/OPIK-2180-add-feature`
- `user/issue-123-fix-bug`
- `user/NA-hotfix-description`

## Commit Format
`[OPIK-####] [COMPONENT] description`
- `[OPIK-1234] [BE] Add create trace endpoint`
- `[OPIK-1234] [FE] Add metrics dashboard`
- `[OPIK-1234] [SDK] Add Python method`
- `[OPIK-1234] [DOCS] Update API documentation`

## PR Title
`[OPIK-####] [COMPONENT] description`

## Never
- Commit directly to main
- Include customer names in commits/PRs
- Commit secrets or .env files
- Force push to main/master
